---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="About the author">
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12 prose-body">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 font-sans">About</h1>
    <div class="mb-12 space-y-6">
      <p lang="zh">我在2026年開始寫作，不是因為有甚麼特別想說的，只是發覺自己都在吸收，輸出太少。我認為每個有認真思考的人，每周都會找到一些想寫的東西，我努力變成那樣。</p>
      
      <p lang="zh">我會寫一些長文，一些讀書筆記，一些順手寫下的。都是我自己寫的，沒有用AI。</p>
      
      <p>I started writing in 2026 — not because I had something particular to say, but because I realized I'd been taking things in without putting much out. I believe anyone who thinks seriously will find something worth writing about each week. I'm trying to become that kind of person.</p>
      
      <p>There will be long essays, reading notes, and things I jot down in passing. I write everything myself, without AI.<br><span class="text-sm text-text-muted italic">(Translated from Chinese with AI though)</span></p>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 font-sans">Experience</h2>
    <dl class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <div>
        <dt class="font-bold">Independent Writer</dt>
        <dd class="text-text-muted mt-1">2020 – Present</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 font-sans">Links</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li><a href="#" class="animated-link text-link hover:text-link-hover">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" class="animated-link text-link hover:text-link-hover">Email</a></li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Base>
